Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.75,0:01:26.41,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,伟尔基姆本来准备\N经由马纽普奇到月球
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.45,0:01:29.48,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,却被迪安娜回归军的炮台\N阻挡了去路
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.89,0:01:33.79,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,格威大人在\N执行强行进攻计划之前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.83,0:01:36.56,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,让我参加炮台爆破小组
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.77,0:01:42.33,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,我们遇到阿迪斯卡王\N向他请求协助
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.37,0:01:47.83,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,结果 我们反而被\N背叛国王的人们抓起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.95,0:01:58.08,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,第三十三话 马纽普奇攻略
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.42,0:01:59.39,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,玛雅莉德
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.85,0:02:01.84,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.63,0:02:09.73,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,民兵的人？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.73,0:02:10.63,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.73,0:02:11.76,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,赶快
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.74,0:02:22.77,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,脱下外衣 得先止血
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.55,0:02:30.11,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,你准备得真周全
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.15,0:02:31.91,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,阿迪斯卡有很多危险的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.95,0:02:33.58,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,看来也是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.62,0:02:37.15,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,顺着水路走就到城市了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.19,0:02:39.22,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,剩下的你自己处理
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.26,0:02:40.49,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,你呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.59,0:02:42.03,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,我要回去国王身边
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.06,0:02:45.36,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,你是马巴族的人\N为何服侍阿迪斯卡王呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.37,0:02:48.03,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,你也是马巴族吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.07,0:02:49.76,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.80,0:02:52.53,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,我只是在三岁之前\N待过马巴族而已
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.57,0:02:54.71,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,阿迪斯卡人攻来时
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.71,0:02:58.41,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,父母被杀的小孩\N都被扔到山麓去了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.45,0:03:01.24,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,我是被叫做西多的\N矿山者捡到 离开这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.28,0:03:02.41,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,那又怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.45,0:03:05.18,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,除了马纽普奇之外\N还有别的城市
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.22,0:03:08.28,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,你可以不用拿武器\N就活下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.32,0:03:10.85,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,服侍国王是我的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.89,0:03:12.55,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,如果库亚多鲁是个好王
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.59,0:03:15.29,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,为何阿迪斯卡人民要\N对国王刀剑相向？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.33,0:03:17.32,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,把国王抓起来？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.36,0:03:20.42,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,阿迪斯卡有阿迪斯卡的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.87,0:03:21.96,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,玛雅莉德
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.00,0:03:23.59,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,赶快走
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.64,0:03:27.20,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,不然你的同伴都会在今夜\N一个不剩的死光
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.75,0:03:42.12,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,库亚多鲁王
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.16,0:03:44.52,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,到祭坛上来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.23,0:03:53.13,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,你还在迷惑吗 塔鲁卡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.27,0:03:59.53,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,如神话所叙述的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.57,0:04:01.40,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,天空变红
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.44,0:04:04.10,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,白色恶魔来拿阿迪斯之枝了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.14,0:04:08.48,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,天与地之间\N巨人们的战争又要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.52,0:04:09.98,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.02,0:04:13.95,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,库亚多鲁王已经\N没能力阻止这场灾难了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.99,0:04:17.92,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,说得对说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.96,0:04:19.89,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,你是被神选上的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.93,0:04:22.42,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,你应该按照自古以来\N的阿迪斯卡传统
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.46,0:04:24.95,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,亲手打倒国王 夺取假面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.00,0:04:27.63,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,成为新的国王
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.34,0:04:30.53,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,不然的话 塔鲁卡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.84,0:04:32.74,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,这个力量不足的国王
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.77,0:04:35.83,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,会为阿迪斯卡之民带来灾害
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.38,0:04:42.61,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,拔剑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.65,0:04:43.75,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.75,0:04:44.91,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.95,0:04:46.92,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,身为国王 这时候我不拔剑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.95,0:04:51.58,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,就从先杀那些人\N拿他们血祭马纽普奇之水
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.69,0:04:53.13,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,为了避开污秽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.16,0:04:55.25,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,只能以污秽来对治
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.07,0:05:00.33,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,你们这些人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.37,0:05:01.73,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,野蛮人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.77,0:05:02.70,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.74,0:05:05.14,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,塔鲁卡 快命令他们住手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.17,0:05:07.57,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,国王你自己先拔剑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.71,0:05:09.61,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,为什么这样做
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.71,0:05:14.31,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,天空染红\N以及我和白色恶魔的出现
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.35,0:05:16.84,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,都不是库亚多鲁王的错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.88,0:05:19.37,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,为什么你不肯搞清楚事情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.42,0:05:22.22,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,为什么要做这么愚蠢的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.26,0:05:25.05,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,我们都是这样子活下来的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.09,0:05:27.82,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,外地人没资格多嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.86,0:05:31.39,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,塔鲁卡 这些人是要破坏\N来自天上的大炮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.43,0:05:33.80,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,拯救这个城市的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.83,0:05:35.96,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,不准相信国王的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.00,0:05:38.10,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,这个国王是为了苟且偷生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.14,0:05:39.77,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,抛弃我们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.81,0:05:41.74,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,到山下去的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.31,0:05:46.28,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,给我剑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.31,0:05:47.44,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,塔鲁卡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.25,0:05:53.69,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,王啊 请拔剑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.72,0:05:56.25,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,我不拔剑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.29,0:05:58.19,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,杀死他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.59,0:06:00.56,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,你们这些人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.59,0:06:01.93,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.70,0:06:07.72,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,在那边
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.77,0:06:08.70,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.14,0:06:10.43,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,不准用剑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.21,0:06:14.50,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,祭坛…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.54,0:06:15.77,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.81,0:06:16.74,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,是火药
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.18,0:06:19.48,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,乔瑟夫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.08,0:06:22.95,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,王呀 拔剑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.62,0:06:24.71,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,现在…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.29,0:06:30.02,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,现在我不拔剑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.06,0:06:32.12,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,为了不让巨人打起来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.16,0:06:34.39,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,我必须帮助外地人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.43,0:06:36.23,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,王啊\N快走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.26,0:06:37.36,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.63,0:06:41.00,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,库亚多鲁王啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.03,0:06:43.30,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,若不把王位交给我们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.34,0:06:45.43,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,阿迪斯卡会灭亡的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.14,0:06:50.11,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,王到底是存何居心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.58,0:06:52.55,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,走右边梯子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.58,0:06:53.98,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,不 那边有士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.01,0:06:55.98,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,我把船开到秘密水路
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.02,0:06:57.04,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.08,0:06:58.11,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,这边
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.69,0:07:09.75,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,不行\N据说他们没到西边梯子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.80,0:07:14.76,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,如果从那里出去\N却没去西边梯子的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.80,0:07:15.93,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,不会吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.97,0:07:17.23,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,过来\N是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.24,0:07:25.27,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,河？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.38,0:07:30.35,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,没路了嘛开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.38,0:07:32.98,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,乔瑟夫\N这个水路是马纽普奇的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.02,0:07:36.46,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,不用说明了\N我们不是来观光旅行的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.49,0:07:39.43,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,你的国王说要开船来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.46,0:07:40.59,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.63,0:07:42.25,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,国王说过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.30,0:07:43.49,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,他不会是逃了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.53,0:07:45.56,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,国王不是那种人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.60,0:07:47.59,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.63,0:07:49.10,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,不请自来的客人来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.14,0:07:50.10,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,数目呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.14,0:07:51.16,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,不多
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.20,0:07:53.23,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,那么不要用火药
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.27,0:07:55.47,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,我也如此打算
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.08,0:08:05.81,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,还有一个逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.85,0:08:07.62,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,去找援兵了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.65,0:08:08.88,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,我猜也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.92,0:08:09.95,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,国王还没来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.99,0:08:11.01,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,马上就来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.06,0:08:12.65,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,不会是逃了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.76,0:08:15.46,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,库亚多鲁王就是那种\N贪生怕死的国王
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.50,0:08:18.16,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,不对 不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.37,0:08:19.99,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,他一拔剑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.03,0:08:21.59,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,就怕死逃跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.64,0:08:24.00,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,这种人不是阿迪斯卡王
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.04,0:08:26.94,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,没想到\N会从你口中听到这句话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.97,0:08:28.17,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,玛雅莉德
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.38,0:08:36.78,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,住手 小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.82,0:08:38.84,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,外人少管闲事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.89,0:08:42.05,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,你再说一次看看\N我就割下你的舌头
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.09,0:08:46.12,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,就算你是大家选上的男人\N我也不会原谅你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.29,0:08:47.73,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,玛雅莉德
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.73,0:08:48.92,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,你想想
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.96,0:08:53.42,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,阿迪斯卡之民一起做了\N天空变红的那个梦的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.87,0:08:58.74,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,新王塔鲁卡！新王塔鲁卡！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.77,0:09:00.83,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,打倒库亚多鲁王
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.87,0:09:03.07,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,为我们带来希望
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.11,0:09:06.91,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,打倒库亚多鲁王\N为我们带来希望…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.95,0:09:12.89,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,你被人们选上 按照规矩\N举剑向旧王库亚多鲁挑战
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.25,0:09:16.52,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,可是 那时候胆怯的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.56,0:09:20.08,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,不是你吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.39,0:09:24.96,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,成为新王的任务是消除灾难\N你若没有办到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.00,0:09:29.30,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,阿迪斯卡人的\N所有希望都会消失
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.77,0:09:35.33,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,那时候\N你害怕背起人民的命运
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.38,0:09:36.77,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.81,0:09:39.64,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,你以为国王没注意到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.68,0:09:41.08,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,他注意到了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.11,0:09:46.42,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,新王塔鲁卡 打倒库亚多鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.45,0:09:48.48,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,王之所以逃走是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.52,0:09:51.15,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,他是为了给你时间
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.19,0:09:54.82,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,等你能够成为真正的\N阿迪斯卡的国王
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.76,0:09:58.73,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,他抱着必死的觉悟\N承受人们的嘲讽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.73,0:10:03.07,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,国王所受的耻辱\N你是不会了解的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.97,0:10:06.50,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,士兵又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.11,0:10:10.08,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,快撞开
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.11,0:10:11.48,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,用巨木吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.51,0:10:12.74,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,完了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.98,0:10:14.17,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,国王是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.25,0:10:16.44,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,国王来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.88,0:10:18.98,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,跳下来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.09,0:10:21.05,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,赶快
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.12,0:10:25.22,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.26,0:10:26.16,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.76,0:10:27.75,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,塔鲁卡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.76,0:10:29.82,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.76,0:10:32.49,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,你没事吧\N他们要逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.07,0:10:37.13,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,玛雅莉德
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.14,0:10:40.23,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,快上船
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.18,0:10:43.44,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,差一点点了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.68,0:10:45.37,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,这边 把手伸长
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.88,0:10:49.61,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,很好 玛雅莉德
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.88,0:10:54.12,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,旧王进入马纽普奇了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.52,0:10:55.89,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.92,0:10:58.55,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,库亚多鲁还不是旧王
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.59,0:11:00.72,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,也不是该死的国王
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.36,0:11:02.85,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,是马纽普奇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.90,0:11:04.02,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.06,0:11:05.12,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.17,0:11:06.26,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,是神殿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.77,0:11:07.96,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,到这里了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.47,0:11:15.27,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,这次不让你上场
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.31,0:11:17.80,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,是因为害怕\N你胸中的炸弹引爆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.84,0:11:19.94,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,会让你成为真正的白色恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.98,0:11:23.14,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.22,0:11:24.91,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,马纽普奇有动向了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.95,0:11:29.82,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,再拖下去 罗兰与艾姆兹\N会被伟尔基姆的炮击炸死
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.86,0:11:31.79,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,天快亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.83,0:11:33.92,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,飞机会开过来吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.63,0:11:36.12,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,我们行动的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.16,0:11:39.15,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,格威大人是不可能\N真的让伟尔基姆开炮的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.20,0:11:40.33,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.37,0:11:43.77,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,那么就出动\N西塞德与加拉比部队吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.77,0:11:45.57,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,赞成
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.01,0:11:47.97,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.24,0:11:52.71,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,这边哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.18,0:11:54.98,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,位置没错吗 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.04,0:12:18.83,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,这么慢才到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.97,0:12:22.07,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,这些人太厉害了\N居然可以夜间着陆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.11,0:12:26.60,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,这十年大家都是这样的\N早就习以为常了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.75,0:12:29.48,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,炸弹搜集到了吗\N差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.06,0:12:44.29,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,这是借船给我的人们的功劳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.33,0:12:46.77,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,各位
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.77,0:12:50.29,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,没有札克的话\N来这里就没有意义了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.34,0:12:52.33,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,炮台在这个方向吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.37,0:12:55.53,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,那座山好像段树木呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.57,0:13:00.01,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,那就是阿迪斯的世界树\N曾经存在的证据
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.05,0:13:04.04,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,神殿左右也有树根痕迹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.08,0:13:06.78,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,天与地的巨人交战
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.82,0:13:10.72,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,砍断的遗迹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.76,0:13:15.75,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,这里真的是天的阶段\N天御虫传说之地呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.79,0:13:16.78,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,罗兰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.83,0:13:21.77,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,不行 被摧毁的神殿前面\N有迪安娜回归军的照明灯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.80,0:13:24.17,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,不过没有人影
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.37,0:13:26.74,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,迪安娜回归军的炮台
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.74,0:13:29.37,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,在北与西边各有三座
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.41,0:13:32.61,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,我和艾姆兹摧毁北边三座
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.64,0:13:34.75,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,罗兰与西多爷负责西边
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.75,0:13:36.94,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,知道吗 西多爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.98,0:13:41.32,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,没问题 但是六座炮台\N必须同时爆炸才行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.35,0:13:45.08,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,那么…还赶得上\N与格威大人约定的时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.12,0:13:47.76,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,那里很难攀爬的 没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.76,0:13:49.16,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,不完成的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.19,0:13:52.49,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,伟尔基姆的炮击会把\N城市与炮台一起摧毁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.53,0:13:56.33,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,不这么做的话\N会被迪安娜回归军欺负着玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.37,0:13:59.46,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,我知道 我带你去西边
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.51,0:14:00.44,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,少年
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.47,0:14:03.24,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,是 拜托你了 库亚多鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.28,0:14:05.57,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,我要陪伴国王
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.61,0:14:07.84,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,那个老头子也拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.32,0:14:13.18,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,你也太多心了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.22,0:14:15.05,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,是不是迷上那个女孩了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.09,0:14:16.52,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.28,0:14:37.47,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,那里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.92,0:14:50.25,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,没有人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.29,0:14:51.45,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,嬴定了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.43,0:15:04.46,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,罗兰 可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.47,0:15:12.00,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,那么 我到隔壁去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.04,0:15:13.34,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.72,0:15:25.35,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,侦察部队传来报告
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.39,0:15:30.52,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,洋上的阿鲁麦亚舰\N向马纽普奇方面开始移动了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.73,0:15:32.59,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,不能再等下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.63,0:15:36.74,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,何雷斯 请准备亿万粒子炮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.74,0:15:37.86,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.90,0:15:41.43,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,纳达拉姆\N请转告战斗机部队去诱敌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.47,0:15:42.57,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.54,0:15:47.57,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,真的要使用主炮？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.61,0:15:49.41,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,必须阻止才行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.88,0:15:53.08,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.29,0:15:55.91,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,喂 喂 我要开门了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.56,0:15:59.55,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.46,0:16:06.80,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.83,0:16:07.92,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,这边也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.97,0:16:09.30,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,剩下的就等罗兰他们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.33,0:16:11.39,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,那里有国王与老爷在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.44,0:16:12.70,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,一定成的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.57,0:16:16.71,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,中止炮击的按键是哪一个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.71,0:16:18.04,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,哪一个？这…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.08,0:16:19.48,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,到底是哪一个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.51,0:16:21.71,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,敌人战舰正向这边过来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.71,0:16:23.31,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,他们的目标是伟尔基姆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.35,0:16:25.21,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,只要撤退就没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.25,0:16:30.02,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,那个城市有马斯特莱\N把船发射到宇宙中的装置
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.06,0:16:31.72,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,马斯特莱？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.76,0:16:34.89,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,得到它的话\N伟尔基姆就能到月球了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.93,0:16:35.95,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,为了这个目的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.99,0:16:39.19,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,罗兰他们与城市的人们\N的死活就可以不顾了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.23,0:16:42.53,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,我跟罗兰他们说过\N黎明时会炮击
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.57,0:16:44.30,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,这时应该已经撤退了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.34,0:16:46.27,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,何雷斯 发炮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.31,0:16:48.27,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,等一下 再等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.31,0:16:49.21,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.24,0:16:53.30,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,西赛德部队与加拉比部队\N在山的坡展开布署了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.35,0:16:55.18,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,我没有出动他们呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.21,0:16:56.44,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,上校大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.48,0:17:00.58,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,我们想让他们\N见识鲁加纳民兵的威力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.69,0:17:04.88,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,快避开
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.29,0:17:06.95,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,发现敌人了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.99,0:17:09.96,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,还有一座炮台没有设置炸药
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.20,0:17:16.50,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,确保罗兰他们的逃亡之路
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.04,0:17:25.84,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,大型炮对准这边了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.94,0:17:29.47,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,大家不要攻击\N全力避开光束
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.32,0:17:36.55,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.26,0:17:43.28,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,阿迪斯卡人民也行动了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.33,0:17:44.73,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,小小的机器木偶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.76,0:17:46.46,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,用岩石就能打倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.50,0:17:49.26,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,我们要拯救\N开拓新道路的旧王
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.30,0:17:51.27,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,塔鲁卡 你愿帮我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.30,0:17:52.74,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,王啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.61,0:17:55.07,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,发射发射
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.58,0:17:58.87,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,苏丝亚 别被打中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.91,0:18:01.17,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,不会啦 这点小炮击
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.35,0:18:09.75,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,美雪小心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.79,0:18:11.59,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,他们看不起飞机
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.62,0:18:13.49,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,不会瞄准我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.89,0:18:16.22,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,利用烟雾靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.26,0:18:21.96,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,国王\N请让炮台的人到外面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.17,0:18:23.36,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.04,0:18:25.00,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,慢着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.04,0:18:26.20,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,你们是何时…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.24,0:18:27.93,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,那边的也举手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.97,0:18:29.37,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,定时器…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.41,0:18:31.00,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,竟然设置这种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.35,0:18:35.61,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.65,0:18:37.38,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,成功了？不
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.42,0:18:39.08,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,还剩下一座炮台
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.12,0:18:40.45,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,你们这些人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.49,0:18:42.54,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,竟然破坏我们的炮台
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.59,0:18:44.45,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.79,0:18:46.62,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,那边也…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.66,0:18:47.68,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,王啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.19,0:18:50.89,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,阿迪斯卡这地方不需要炮台
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.93,0:18:52.95,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,你们这些迷信的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.83,0:18:55.30,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,玛雅莉德
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.33,0:18:56.49,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,玛雅莉德小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.54,0:18:57.63,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,滚！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.94,0:18:59.90,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.94,0:19:00.93,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.97,0:19:03.60,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,别让机器兵靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.65,0:19:08.74,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,发射
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.22,0:19:13.38,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,罗兰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.32,0:19:18.19,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,你说你要把染红空中的炸弹\N扔到宇宙是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.22,0:19:20.25,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,是的 我说过
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.29,0:19:22.52,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,你一定要完成誓言
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.56,0:19:23.93,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.26,0:19:26.66,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,哇 您做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.97,0:19:29.37,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,库亚多鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.40,0:19:32.77,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,玛雅莉德\N你也跟那个少年走
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.14,0:19:39.24,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,塔鲁卡 杀死我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.09,0:19:50.15,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,库亚多鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.19,0:19:52.28,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,王啊库亚多鲁王
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.32,0:19:58.16,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,你应该遵守阿迪斯卡的规矩\N为新时代除旧！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.20,0:19:59.42,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,王啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.46,0:20:02.92,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,现在塔鲁卡有资格杀我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.90,0:20:07.10,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,我承认\N塔鲁卡已经有杀我的资格了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.14,0:20:08.47,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,王啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.51,0:20:11.64,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,不要犹豫 不要迷惑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.74,0:20:13.80,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,塔鲁卡 这是王的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.65,0:20:18.84,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,王啊\N我假阿迪斯之枝之名…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.88,0:20:19.98,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,塔鲁卡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.75,0:20:21.91,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,玛雅莉德
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.95,0:20:24.75,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,你才是真正的新王
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.79,0:20:26.31,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,让我陪你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.43,0:20:32.36,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,为什么交替的重大时刻\N玛雅莉德会在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.54,0:20:39.90,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,请抓住阿迪斯卡之枝\N到天上去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.94,0:20:41.20,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,到天上去…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.78,0:20:51.48,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,居然…玛雅莉德…\N你居然做到这种程度
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.15,0:20:54.81,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,库亚多鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.85,0:20:58.15,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,登上树枝 成为老鹰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.73,0:21:05.09,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,我们明日的生命\N都获得保障了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.93,0:21:11.13,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,马纽普奇陷落了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.17,0:21:12.73,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,好像是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.77,0:21:14.24,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,跟着黎明一起到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.85,0:21:26.31,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,阿迪斯卡之民的新王啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.09,0:21:31.99,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,伟大的旧王 库亚多鲁\N可是从来不哭的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.33,0:21:43.77,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,别在意啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.00,0:21:47.60,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,我居然没办法为她做任何事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.31,0:21:50.17,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,库亚多鲁说过
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.21,0:21:52.87,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,白色恶魔要来拿阿迪斯之枝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.91,0:21:55.61,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,我们的神话到那里就结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.71,0:21:56.84,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.88,0:22:01.01,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,那就是阿迪斯之枝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.49,0:22:05.55,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,库亚多鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.59,0:22:08.39,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,我一定会借着阿迪斯之枝\N札克特雷卡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.43,0:22:14.19,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,驾驶着你所称的新巨人\N白色恶魔WHITE DOLL
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.23,0:22:16.93,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,把核弹扔到宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.12,0:23:43.76,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,伟尔·基姆留下的船只\N飞上宇宙的那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.76,0:23:46.05,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,宝中尉也追击过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.09,0:23:49.93,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,可是\NWHITDOLL胸中埋着核弹
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.96,0:23:52.09,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,我不能随意开动它
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.13,0:23:56.83,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,因为我不愿意让我的MS\N变成真正的白色恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.87,0:24:00.39,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,下集TURN A高达
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.44,0:24:02.74,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,飞行到成层圈
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.77,0:24:05.00,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,风吹向宇宙…
